data.description: Sitting on the northwest edge of Fairbury across from North Park with the walking trail, soccer fields, pickle ball courts and swimming pool is this beautiful 5 bedroom, 3.5 bath ranch home with oversized 2 car attached garage and fenced in back yard waiting for you. When you access the home you will walk into the great room that includes the family room and dining area with patio, Heat and Glow gas fireplace and open staircase to the lower level. Fully applianced kitchen. Main floor utility. Three bedrooms on the main level includes the master bedroom with walk-in closet and bath with Jacuzzi tub and separate shower. Lower level has huge family room, two bedrooms, bath, storage room and egress windows. In 2019 it was updated with new laminate flooring,  a new  roof, new siding, all new replacement windows and new garage door. Whole house generator. Solid 6 panel doors throughout. This home is ready for you to move in.
